data.description:
Fantastic Opportunity to get into one of Madison County's most attractive neighborhoods in this lightly lived-in home! This house has a perfect open floorplan layout , amazing landscaping featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 baths and a nice sized office. 12 foot celiings, crown molding, and generous sized living room with fireplace. 
Real hardwood flooring. Kitchen features quartz countertops, stainless appliances and abundance of cabinets. Primary bedroom has tray ceilings and ensuite spacious bath with large shower. Great sized backyard, and huge patio area that backs up to the treeline that gives you extra privacy. Come see it today!
